## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity and nuances of the SDGs' implementation and impact. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of global challenges means that the relevance and effectiveness of the SDGs may change over time, necessitating ongoing evaluation and adaptation. Furthermore, the report does not include primary data or firsthand accounts from stakeholders involved in the implementation of the SDGs, which could provide deeper insights into their practical challenges and successes.

